.tool-bar {
  background-color: #313437;
  border: 1px solid #414346;
  color: #9d9e9f;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: flex-start;
}
.tool-bar button.tool-bar-btn {
  background-color: #313437;
  background-image: inherit;
  border-color: #313437;
  cursor: pointer;
  flex: 0 0 auto;
  margin: 2px;
  padding: 0;
}
.tool-bar button.tool-bar-btn:before {
  display: inline;
}
.tool-bar button.tool-bar-btn:focus,
.tool-bar button.tool-bar-btn:hover {
  border-color: #9d9e9f;

}

  margin-left: 0;
}
.tool-bar.tool-bar-vertical .tool-bar-btn + .tool-bar-btn {

}
.tool-bar.tool-bar-horizontal .tool-bar-spacer {
  border: 0 none;

  border-right: 1px solid #9d9e9f;
  margin: 5px 0;
}
.tool-bar.tool-bar-vertical .tool-bar-spacer {
  border: 0 none;

}
